<div class="article-container">
    <h2 style="text-align: center; color: cyan;">Vacancy: We're Hiring! Social Media Manager, Blogger, and Graphic Designer</h2>
    <p>At 9jamix, we are looking for talented and creative individuals to join our dynamic team. If you are passionate about social media, writing, or graphic design, we have exciting opportunities for you. We are hiring for the following positions:</p>

    <h3>1. Social Media Manager</h3>
    <p><strong>Job Description:</strong> As a Social Media Manager, you will be responsible for creating and managing social media campaigns, building brand awareness, and engaging with our community across various platforms.</p>
    <p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Develop and execute social media strategies for brand growth.</li>
        <li>Manage social media accounts, including Instagram, Twitter, Facebook, and others.</li>
        <li>Create, curate, and share engaging content.</li>
        <li>Monitor, analyze, and report on social media performance.</li>
        <li>Engage with followers, respond to comments, and foster a positive community.</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Experience Required:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Minimum 2 years of experience in social media management.</li>
        <li>Proven track record of successful social media campaigns.</li>
        <li>Strong knowledge of social media platforms and trends.</li>
        <li>Excellent communication and creative writing skills.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>2. Blogger</h3>
    <p><strong>Job Description:</strong> We are looking for a creative and skilled Blogger to produce high-quality content that engages and informs our audience. Your articles will cover a range of topics, from music to entertainment and lifestyle.</p>
    <p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Write and publish articles regularly on topics related to music, news, and entertainment.</li>
        <li>Research trending topics and provide fresh, insightful content.</li>
        <li>Collaborate with the editorial team to develop content ideas.</li>
        <li>Ensure all content is optimized for SEO.</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Experience Required:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>At least 1-2 years of experience in blogging or content writing.</li>
        <li>Strong writing, editing, and proofreading skills.</li>
        <li>Familiarity with SEO and keyword research tools.</li>
        <li>Experience in writing for digital platforms is a plus.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>3. Graphic Designer</h3>
    <p><strong>Job Description:</strong> We are looking for a talented Graphic Designer to create visually appealing graphics for our website, social media platforms, and marketing materials.</p>
    <p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Design engaging and effective graphics for social media, websites, and print.</li>
        <li>Collaborate with the marketing and content teams to understand design needs.</li>
        <li>Ensure that all graphics align with the brand’s identity and message.</li>
        <li>Stay updated with design trends and incorporate them into your work.</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Experience Required:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Proven experience as a graphic designer, with a strong portfolio of work.</li>
        <li>Proficiency in design software such as Adobe Photoshop, Illustrator, and InDesign.</li>
        <li>Strong creative vision with attention to detail.</li>
        <li>Experience in web design and social media content is a plus.</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Why Join Us?</h3>
    <p>We offer competitive salaries and benefits to all our employees. At 9jamix, we foster a creative and inclusive work environment where your ideas and contributions are valued. If you’re looking to join a dynamic team and make an impact, we want to hear from you!</p>

    <h3>How to Apply:</h3>
          <p>Interested candidates can apply by sending their resumes and portfolios (for designers) to <strong>edabystudios@gmail.com</strong>. Please specify the position you are applying for in the subject line. We look forward to having you join our team!</p>
</div>

